=== 盖·福克斯面具 ===
{{main|盖·福克斯面具}}
[[File:London_QVS_April_12_2008_0010_Anons.jpg|right]]，摄于2008年的伦敦。]]
影片上映后，书及影片中出现的[[蓋·福克斯面具|蓋·福克斯面具]]每年都卖出数千份<ref>{{cite news |title=Story and Symbol: V for Vendetta and OWS |url=https://www.psychologytoday.com/gb/blog/how-fantasy-becomes-reality/201111/story-and-symbol-v-vendetta-and-ows |work=Psychology Today |date=2011-11-04 |accessdate=2020-08-22 |archive-date=2020-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822064306/https://www.psychologytoday.com/gb/blog/how-fantasy-becomes-reality/201111/story-and-symbol-v-vendetta-and-ows |dead-url=no }}</ref>。持有影片版权[[时代华纳|时代华纳]]斥资销售官方正版面具<ref>{{cite news| url=http://newsfeed.time.com/2011/08/29/how-time-warner-profits-from-the-anonymous-hackers/| title=How Time Warner Profits from the 'Anonymous' Hackers| last=Carbone| first=Nick| work=Time| date=2011-08-29| accessdate=2011-08-30| archive-date=2017-12-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224201558/http://newsfeed.time.com/2011/08/29/how-time-warner-profits-from-the-anonymous-hackers/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nickbilton">{{cite news|last=Bilton|first=Nick|title=Masked Protesters Aid Time Warner's Bottom Line|work=The New York Times|date=2011-08-28|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/29/technology/masked-anonymous-protesters-aid-time-warners-profits.html|accessdate=2012-07-20|archive-date=2012-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120507000148/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/29/technology/masked-anonymous-protesters-aid-time-warners-profits.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

蓋・福克斯面具已经成为了公认的反政权标志，曾出现在许多反政府示威活动亮相，包括2008年抗议[[山达基教会|山达基教会]]的{{le|Chanology行动|Operation Chanology}}<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20213067_20213068_20213004_5,00.html|title=Alan Moore Still Knows the Score!|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|last=Gopalan|first=Nisha|date=2008-07-21|access-date=2010-09-24|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110215084708/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20213067_20213068_20213004_5,00.html|archivedate=2011-02-15}}</ref>、[[2011年埃及革命|2011年埃及革命]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jadaliyya.com/pages/index/1723/v-for-vendetta_the-other-face-of-egypts-youth-move |title="V for Vendetta": The Other Face of Egypt's Youth Movement |date=2011-05-30 |first=Linda |last=Herrera |website=Jadaliyya |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107022311/http://www.jadaliyya.com/pages/index/1723/v-for-vendetta_the-other-face-of-egypts-youth-move |archivedate=2013-11-07 |accessdate=2020-08-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[占领华尔街|占领华尔街]]等[[占领运动|占领运动]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/nsw/v-for-vague-occupy-sydneys-faceless-leaders-20111014-1loy6.html|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=2011-10-14|title=V for vague: Occupy Sydney's faceless leaders|dead-url=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622170039/http://www.smh.com.au/nsw/v-for-vague-occupy-sydneys-faceless-leaders-20111014-1loy6.html|archivedate=2012-06-22|accessdate=2020-08-22}}</ref>、香港[[雨伞革命|雨伞革命]]<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-29928849|title = HK protesters scuffle with police|work = BBC News|date = 2014-11-06|accessdate = 2020-08-22|archive-date = 2020-03-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200302033807/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-china-29928849|dead-url = no}}</ref>及[[反修例运动|反修例运动]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Hong Kong protesters defy the mask ban – in pictures |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/gallery/2019/oct/07/hong-kong-protesters-defy-the-mask-ban-in-pictures |website=The Guardians |accessdate=2020-08-22 |date=2019-10-07 |archive-date=2020-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416102041/https://www.theguardian.com/world/gallery/2019/oct/07/hong-kong-protesters-defy-the-mask-ban-in-pictures |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

